== PANDUAN MENJALANKAN CHECKO TODOLIST ==
== VERSI PostgreSQL Neon (ForHosting) ==

PERSIAPAN (sekali saja):
1. Install Go (golang.org/dl)
2. Install Git (git-scm.com)
3. Clone repo: git clone https://github.com/afdalaziz52/todolist1.git
4. Masuk folder: cd todolist1
5. Pindah branch: git checkout ForHosting
6. Download dependency: go mod tidy
7. Isi file .env:
   DATABASE_URL=postgresql://neondb_owner:npg_OKUjq3wEvHt7@ep-bitter-math-akx6btjn-pooler.c-3.us-west-2.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require&channel_binding=require
   JWT_SECRET=rahasia_jwt_kamu
   PORT=8081
   APP_NAME=apk_todolist
   APP_ENV=development

MENJALANKAN APP:
1. Buka terminal di folder project
2. Ketik: go run main.go
3. Buka browser: http://localhost:8081

HOSTING SEMENTARA:
1. Download cloudflared atau jalankan:
   curl -L https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflared/releases/latest/download/cloudflared-windows-amd64.exe -o cloudflared.exe
2. Pastikan go run main.go sudah jalan di terminal 1
3. Buka terminal baru, ketik:
   ./cloudflared.exe tunnel --url http://localhost:8081
4. Copy URL yang muncul (https://xxxx.trycloudflare.com)
5. URL berubah setiap kali dijalankan ulang
6. App hanya online selama laptop nyala

DATABASE:
- Pakai Neon PostgreSQL (online, tidak perlu install lokal)
- Lihat data: console.neon.tech → Tables atau SQL Editor
- Undang rekan: Settings → People → Invite member

